*** '''Player:''' Does this mean the Wintertodt won't be a threat anymore?
*** '''Undor:''' That should be the case in the long run. I suspect it will take a long time though. The Doors were damaged for a while and the Wintertodt will have gained a lot of power.
*** '''Undor:''' I reckon that magic lot will have to do their fiery tricks for a bit longer before everything is back to normal.
*** '''Undor:''' Anyway, I'll get to work fixing the Doors. You should head back to Lady Lovakengj and let her know that the problem has been solved.
*** {{tact|end}}
