===Returning to Lady Lovakengj===
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' The human seems a bit lost Councillor. Could you help them please.
* '''Player:''' But I've done what you asked!
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Oh. What did I ask?
* '''Councillor Unkar:''' We asked them to go and see what help Undor needed at the Doors of Dinh.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' That we did Councillor. Quite right. And what was it that Undor needed?
* '''Player:''' Undor had found some damage caused to the Doors of Dinh. He suspected someone had sabotaged them. He asked me to fetch him Dinh's Hammer so that he could fix the Doors.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' And?
* '''Player:''' I found the hammer and gave it to Undor. He should be fixing the Doors as we speak.
* '''Councillor Unkar:''' Well this is excellent news. With the Doors fixed, the Wintertodt poses a far smaller threat to Kourend. Well done.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Yes, yes, wonderful stuff. I think I'll have a sherry to celebrate.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Jorra! Bring me a sherry.
* '''Jorra:''' Yes Lady Lovakengj.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' ...
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Councillor, why is the human still here?
* '''Councillor Unkar:''' I think they want a reward, Lady Lovakengj.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' A reward?
* '''Councillor Unkar:''' Yes, Lady Lovakengj.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Oh.
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Well here you go, have this then.
* {{Qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
* '''Lady Vulcana Lovakengj:''' Oh. The human is still here.
* {{tact|(Non-quest dialogue.)}}

